<item>
            <title>[LU-17484] Do not resend SEC_CTX_INIT RPCs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17484</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Requests that are initializing GSS security contexts cannot be resent to failover NIDs, as they contain information specific to the remote peer NID. If they are resent to a different NID, GSS will reject them anyway.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
